steps.html_instructions: Head east on Center St NE toward Church St NE
Merge onto I-5 S via the ramp to Eugene
Take the State Route 66/State Route 140 ramp to Lakeview/Medford

Turn left onto OR-140 E/OR-66 E
Continue to follow OR-140 E

Turn left onto CA-36 E/Main St
Continue to follow CA-36 E
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-80 E/Sparks/Elko and merge onto I-80 E
Take exit 48 toward US-95 Alt/US-50 Alt/E Fernley
Turn right onto I-80BUS W/US-95 ALT (signs for Fernley/Fallon/NAS Fallon)

At the traffic circle, take the 3rd exit onto US 30/E Main St
Continue to follow US 30

Turn left onto US-95 S/S 2nd St/Rte 95 S
Continue to follow US-95 S/Rte 95 S
Take exit 75B to merge onto N Casino Center Blvd toward Downtown LV

Turn left onto S Las Vegas Blvd
Destination will be on the right
